                    <span>Having read several similar titles I would say that this highly readable book is perhaps the best I have come across. Flood brings the important strands together in easily manageable chapters, and includes much imortant recent scholarship.<br>To link this book or its author to an 'orientalist' agenda (as an earlier reviewer appears to) is frankly ridiculous.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Not Too Shabby</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
